name: USGSAlleghenyRiverKittanningWaterLevelReport
0:
”Alexa, open USGS Water Monitor.”
”Alexa, ask USGS Water Monitor what the water level in Kittanning is.”
”Alexa, ask USGS Water Monitor how high the water is.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: u. s. g. s. water monitor
des: This skill will respond with the most recent USGS water level reading from site 03036501, the Allegheny river Kittanning lower pool. Skill icon by Freepik on Flaticon.com CC BY 3.0. Unaffiliated with the USGS.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
